===Intransitive verb===
'''rotate''' ('''rotates''', '''rotated''', '''rotating''')
#to [[spin]], [[turn]], or [[revolve]]
#:''He '''rotated''' in his chair to face me.''

===Transitive verb===
#to spin, turn, or revolve something
#:'''''Rotate''' the dial to the left.''
#to [[replace]] older materials or to place older materials in front of newer ones so that older ones get used first
#:''The supermarket '''rotates''' the stock daily so that old foods don't sit around.''
#(''of [[tire]]s'') to change which tire is on each corner of the car, so that they wear evenly
#:'''''Rotate''' your tires every 15,000 miles.''